pageProduct.name: Skin Republic 24k Gold Under Eye Patches
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Aquagel under eye patches infused with 24K Gold reduce crow’s feet and fine lines. Provide a continuous and concentrated dose of antiaging serum to the delicate eye area.

- Light reflecting Gold particles conceal the signs of aging

- Collagen and Adenosine help improve the skin’s elasticity and minimise the appearance of fine lines.

- Antioxidants and Phytonutrients found in Blueberries nourish for bright, younger looking eyes.

Ingredients

AQUA/WATER/EAU, DIPROPYLENE GLYCOL, GLYCERIN, 1,2-HEXANEDIOL, CERATONIA SILIQUA GUM, CHONDRUS CRISPUS POWDER, MICA, POLYACRYLATE-13, CELLULOSE GUM, POLYISOBUTENE, EUTERPE OLERACEA FRUIT EXTRACT, ADENOSINE, POLYSORBATE 20, BUTYLENE GLYCOL, DISODIUM EDTA, HYDROLYZED COLLAGEN, VACCINIUM ANGUSTIFOLIUM (BLUEBERRY) FRUIT EXTRACT, ASPALATHUS LINEARIS EXTRACT, PORTULACA OLERACEA EXTRACT, CARTHAMUS TINCTORIUS FLOWER EXTRACT, ROSA RUGOSA FLOWER EXTRACT, PAEONIA ALBIFLORA FLOWER EXTRACT, CITRUS PARADISI FRUIT EXTRACT, PHENOXYETHANOL, TITANIUM DIOXIDE (CI 77891), IRON OXIDES (CI 77491), GOLD

Directions

Cleanse skin. Place one patch below each eye area. After 30 minutes, remove patches. Do not rinse
